{"tid":142023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【急尋】16歲少女汪洛伊失蹤逾個半月 警呼籲巿民留意","createTime":"2017-03-03T11:47:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-03T17:38:30.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a49f3b6ce997019d5b9d79c44ef38c197be2d684","tid":142023,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T11:47:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170303/large/1488539599_b55e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170303%2Flarge%2F1488539599_b55e.jpg&h=3346d746&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n16歲女童汪洛伊於1月14日離開其位於彩德邨的住所後便告失蹤，其家人於翌日向警方報案。她身高約1.61米，體重約50公斤，中等身材，圓面型，黃皮膚，蓄藍綠色長直髮。她最後露面時身穿黑白色上衣、藍色褲及黑色運動鞋。警方呼籲任何人士如有該失蹤女童的消息或曾見過她，請致電3661 0316或電郵至rmpu-ke-2@police.gov.hk 與東九龍總區失蹤人口調查組，或與任何一間警署聯絡。"},{"pid":"dbdbae982a5fc29ff63f9f1a283704836bb7b897","tid":142023,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T12:02:57.000Z","msg":"好似萬二蚊"},{"pid":"435c5308f0d52e9076ac0220e8c15b2a7a3773c8","tid":142023,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T12:03:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ccdedaf759da46df14c92732881790be53716878","tid":142023,"uid":1134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T12:04:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似萬二蚊</blockquote><br />\n驗眼驗腦啦屌你老母臭閪"},{"pid":"964e092f389b9522f848fd9aa2a4e8a54022f80b","tid":142023,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T12:11:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>{{{0}}}</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a46645aabbab9793d9b63b9ada53b82347c83bf9","tid":142023,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T12:33:40.000Z","msg":"可能係某個警署"},{